videos.description: De'Anthony Melton makes the three point jumper off the assist from Jonah Mathews
videos.headline: USC using 3-point shooting to keep pace with Oregon

videos.description: Chris Boucher drives the lane and throws down a massive dunk.
videos.headline: Chris Boucher throws it down with authority

videos.description: Chimezie Metu drives the lane and hammers home a huge two handed jam.
videos.headline: Metu punishes the rim with huge two handed slam

videos.description: After USC threw down a big dunk, Chris Boucher finishes a huge alley-oop dunk on the next trip down the court for Oregon.
videos.headline: Boucher throws down huge alley-oop dunk

videos.description: USC head coach Andy Enfield talks about the intensity by both teams in the first half.
videos.headline: Halftime Interview with USC head coach Andy Enfield

videos.description: Elijah Stewart throws down an alley-oop passed from half-court.
videos.headline: Stewart throws down huge alley-oop

videos.description: Oregon makes 3-pointers on three straight possessions in the second-half.
videos.headline: Oregon finding 3-point shooting in the second half

videos.description: Dillon Brooks picks up his fifth foul with over three minutes remaining in a close game
videos.headline: Brooks fouls out down the stretch in close game

videos.description: Tyler Dorsey transition 3 down the stretch gives Oregon a comfortable lead.
videos.headline: Dorsey 3-point shot gives Oregon comfortable lead down the stretch
Metu picks up flagrant foul in final 15 seconds
